          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下王君可。父亲王俊，当日在朝拜中郎大将，不幸早丧，因此隐住林下。想\n俺一身武艺，无有引荐，不能出头。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "王君可",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个明珠土内藏，不知何日放毫光？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王君可",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "豪杰生平时未来，\n乌云遮住栋梁才。\n走尽天涯无处栽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王君可下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 6
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "土地"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（土地上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "土地土地，有些灵气。若还不灵，枉为土地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃土地是也。今有杨国贞有数载难处，不免使动神虎，将她君臣冲散。\n猛虎何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（虎形上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾命你将杨国贞君臣冲散，不可伤她性命。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "土地",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾神若不明指引，误了凡间许多人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（土地、虎形同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "念": 1,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "李广",
        "杨国贞",
        "王君可"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李广、杨国贞同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我好比出林鸟又招弹打，\n到如今四路逃奔走天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳边厢又听得风声响亮，\n想必是有大虫跑下山岗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军，将军！\n不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中途路失散了李广将，\n好似钢刀刺胸膛。\n凭天由命在何方。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨国贞下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘娘，国母！\n哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中途路失散了龙国后，\n好似钢刀刺咽喉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众手下 （内同白） 金盔金甲是李广。上前拿住。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂呀，方才有人讲到，捉拿金盔金甲李广，这便怎么处？\n也罢！不免将盔铠放在此处罢。\n哎，国母啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李广卸甲两泪汪，\n中途路上失皇娘。\n准备人马破庆阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李广",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉命侯李广题。\n国母吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李广下。王君可上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王君可",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，十字路口有金盔甲，待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王君可",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李广卸甲两泪汪，中途路上失皇娘。有人收了盔和甲，准备人马破庆阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王君可",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉命侯李广题。\n原来是李大人卸甲逃走。俺不免收了，后来也有出头之日也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王君可下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "杨国贞→李广",
          "turns": 2
        },
        {
          "edge": "李广→杨国贞",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "李广→王君可",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 10,
          "唱": 2,
          "白": 4
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.333,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "女娲",
        "杨国贞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四神将、四龙套、金童、玉女、生婆、城隍、土地、女娲同上。〖点绛唇〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "女娲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "双扇龙门单扇开，今奉玉旨下天台。珍珠帘笼金钩挂，威威闪开女娲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "女娲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾女娲娘娘是也。今有杨国贞，身怀后朝阙龙，来在吾神殿前，须要护拥。\n众神将，各显神威。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨国贞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天涯行走无处奔，\n腹内疼痛路难行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是女娲庙，待我进去歇息再走。\n哎呀娘娘吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨国贞双膝跪埃尘，\n娘娘菩萨显威灵。\n满炉焚香谢上神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "腹内疼痛为何情？\n十月怀胎要降生。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨国贞生。生婆、城隍、土地、四云童同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我好比睡梦人方才醒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来生下小姣生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨国贞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且喜生下后朝阙龙，不免拜过娘娘，天涯逃生去罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨国贞下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "女娲→杨国贞",
          "turns": 1
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 12,
          "念": 1,
          "唱": 2
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.667,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "狐仙"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（狐仙上，跳。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "狐仙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "银牙一咬赛钢钉，赤脸红发火焰生。修行千年为道行，要作蓬莱洞中人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "狐仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾乃千年狐仙是也。曾在半架山修炼千百馀年，今有杨国贞生下后朝阙龙，因"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 3,
          "念": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘玉英",
        "四丫鬟"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（青水会。刘玉英上，四丫鬟同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绣花绣鸳鸯，风吹菊花香。三月桃花放，九月菊花黄。\n一般根在土，各自等时光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家刘玉英。爹爹刘百万。家产有百万之富，单生奴家一人。每日绣楼习学针\n黹，今日闷闷不乐，不免去到花园散闷。\n丫鬟，带路花园。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四丫鬟",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一寸光阴一寸金，\n寸金难买寸光阴。\n失却光阴哪里寻。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（狐仙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四丫鬟",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳边厢又听得有人声，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只见丫鬟面前存。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四丫鬟",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐这是为何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘玉英",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫丫鬟带路回绣房，\n神思恍忽为哪桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘玉英、四丫鬟同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "刘玉英→四丫鬟",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "四丫鬟→刘玉英",
          "turns": 3
        }
      ],
